Manage AGH sessions

Usage:
  agh session [command]

Available Commands:
  events      Read session events
  health      Read session health and wake eligibility
  history     Show session history grouped by turn
  inspect     Inspect session health, wake audit, and policy correlation
  list        List sessions
  new         Create a new session
  prompt      Send a prompt to a session
  repair      Inspect and repair an interrupted session transcript
  resume      Resume a stopped session
  soul        Manage session Soul snapshots
  status      Show session status
  stop        Stop a session
  wait        Block until a session stops

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for session

Global Flags:
      --json            Emit JSON output
  -o, --output string   Output format: human, json, jsonl, or toon (default "human")

Use "agh session [command] --help" for more information about a command.
